<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/792116-her-baby-when-she-has-the-baby-they">....her baby. When she has the baby, they tell her that her baby died and show her a body of a baby girl. She goes on with her life and many years later is told that there is a teaching job available as a tudor to some children of a Prince or King? over seas. She accepts job. She later realizes that the man is the duke she fell in love with and that he did not die. Also the child she had was not dead and was a boy.</a>
