  <span id="freeText5337572237368075427" style="display:none">This is not usually a book I would pick up but I remember a friend of mine giving it to me to read but I had never finished it. I had fond memories of it, so when I found it at the goodwill, practically in pieces too, I gave it a shot and couldn't be more glad that I did! Though this book is quite old, it delivers a slamming story. I would say this is romance with lots of mystery as I couldn't figure out what was going on until it was practically laid out for me at the end. I so enjoyed this book and plan to read more of her this year. Pb's are easily found, so that's good. 5 moons for me!</span>
