        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2037277205" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13206015518434582851"><b>Actual Rating: 2.5 Stars</b><br/><br/>I&apos;m giving this book a very mid-ranged rating, because while it had a frustratingly over-dramatic romance, a frustratingly one-tracked heroine, and a frustratingly exasperating set of characters... well, the book was addictively engrossing.<br/><br/>I couldn&apos;t keep myself from wondering about what had happened to Helena, or what would happen to Helena... even while the entire ordeal was completely predictable.<br/><br/>I disliked a lot of the characters, and I disliked how blasé Frau Graber </span>
  <span id="freeText13206015518434582851" style="display:none"><b>Actual Rating: 2.5 Stars</b><br><br>I'm giving this book a very mid-ranged rating, because while it had a frustratingly over-dramatic romance, a frustratingly one-tracked heroine, and a frustratingly exasperating set of characters... well, the book was addictively engrossing.<br><br>I couldn't keep myself from wondering about what had happened to Helena, or what would happen to Helena... even while the entire ordeal was completely predictable.<br><br>I disliked a lot of the characters, and I disliked how blasé Frau Graber treated all the deaths, attempted murders, deception, lies, betrayals, and indifference of the nobility to these events; blowing them off as it being simply the culture in their country, and that everything was just about "state affair" and nothing to get worked up about. Boy, that was frustrating to get through that last half of the book.<br><br>Really, the only thing going for this book was the beautiful writing, the imagery, the description, and a lot of the lore and history laid within the book's world.<br><br>Anyway, I may or may not come back and give a proper review.<br><br>I read this book for <b>
  <a href="https://anicheungbookabyss.blogspot.com/p/halloween-bingo-2017.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Halloween Bingo 2017</a>
</b>.<br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1505608842i/23940647.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br></span>
